metadata.label: Summary (English)
metadata.value: This manuscript contains a collection of computistic and astronomical texts, as well as medical recipes in German (Alemannic) and Latin. Among the identified texts there are excerpts from the Buch der Natur by Konrad von Megenberg. Spaces intended for decorations and perhaps for illustrations have remained blank.

metadata.label: Persons
metadata.value: Author: Conradus, de Megenberg; Former possessor: Falck, Peter; Librarian: Gremaud, Jean
